<h1>Root Component UI </h1>
<h2>Two Way Data binding, Ex-01</h2>
Enter Name at source:
<input type="text" [(ngModel)]='name'> <hr/>
Name: {{name}} <hr/>

Enter Name at target:
<input type="text" [(ngModel)]='name'> <hr/>


--------------------------

<h1>Root Component UI </h1>
<h2>Two Way Data binding, Ex-02</h2>
Enter No:
<input type="number" [(ngModel)]='n' /> <br/>
{{"Given no is: "+n}} <br/>
{{"Square of "+n+" is: "+(n*n)}} <br/>

-----------------
<h1>Root Component UI </h1>
<h2>Two Way Data binding, Ex-03</h2>
Enter No1:
<input type="number" [(ngModel)]='a' /> <br/>

Enter No2:
<input type="number" [(ngModel)]='b' /> <br/>
{{"a = "+a+", b = "+b}} <br/>
{{"Add of "+a+" and "+b+" is: "+(a+b)}} <br/>
{{"Sub of "+a+" and "+b+" is: "+(a-b)}} <br/>
{{"Mult of "+a+" and "+b+" is: "+(a*b)}} <br/>
{{"Div of "+a+" and "+b+" is: "+(a/b)}} <br/>

========================
<h1>Root Component UI </h1>
<h2>Two Way Data binding, Ex-04</h2>
Choose Gender:
<input type="radio" [(ngModel)]='gender' value="Mr."> Male
<input type="radio" [(ngModel)]='gender' value="Miss."> Female <br/>

Hello {{gender}}

=======================

<h1>Root Component UI </h1>
<h2>Two Way Data binding, Ex-05</h2>

<input type="checkbox" [(ngModel)]='terms'> Terms and conditions <hr/>
{{terms}}

======================

<h1>Root Component UI </h1>
<h2>Two Way Data binding, Ex-06</h2>

Choose Direction
<select [(ngModel)]='direction'>
    <option value="North">North</option>
    <option value="East">East</option>
    <option value="West">West</option>
    <option value="South">South</option>
</select> {{direction}}
==========================
